4
00:00:23.664 --> 00:00:25.665
<v Daniel>Glad to be here for this one. It's a wild topic.</v>

5
00:00:25.950 --> 00:00:39.483
<v Maya>It really is. Our mission today is to explore exactly how artificial intelligence is just fundamentally rewiring the service industry. And we're looking at this for you, the listener, because, well, it's completely changing the services you interact with every single day.</v>

6
00:00:39.683 --> 00:00:44.908
<v Daniel>Yeah. And it's important to realize this isn't just that old story about robots replacing humans.</v>

7
00:00:45.048 --> 00:00:56.362
