8
00:00:56.542 --> 00:01:05.734
<v Daniel>The whole dynamic is shifting from AI being this passive tool we use to AI being an active participant in the service itself. It just changes the entire equation.</v>

9
00:01:06.143 --> 00:01:18.153
<v Maya>It does. And to make sense of this, we are looking at a really fantastic stack of sources today. We have a theoretical paper establishing a brand new framework for understanding these human interactions.</v>

10
00:01:18.193 --> 00:01:20.115
<v Daniel>Which is super helpful for getting the big picture.</v>

11
00:01:20.415 --> 00:01:35.088
